agus Risotto","step":0},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Place Parmesan in mixing bowl and grate <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","step":9},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Place asparagus stalk pieces, shallots and oil in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then sauté <b>3 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>.","step":10},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Add wine then risotto rice and, without measuring cup, cook <b>2 min\/120°C\/\/speed 1<b>. Scrape base of mixing bowl with spatula to loosen rice.","step":11},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Add hot stock, salt and pepper. Place Varoma dish into position and weigh in peas. Cover then cook <b>12-15 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b> until rice is cooked al dente (with a bite) - the risotto should be slightly soupy at this stage.","step":12},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Set Varoma aside. Add reserved asparagus tips, reserved Parmesan and butter then stir in with spatula. Adjust seasoning if desired then replace Varoma and leave to rest for 2 minutes.","step":13},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Serve with peas on the side accompanied by the tear and share rolls.","step":14}],"usefulItems":"bowl, serving bowls, large baking tray, freezer-proof container, pastry brush, oven","id":"r218852","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-pyFan6LRmpo\/XZVPyX6UA-I\/AAAAAAAAc8k\/tXRP9IClVTA2tf7KzYEqyTl78VAH_ZL5wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_EoH95SJlL_BhXmTk.png","title":"Asparagus Risotto, Sun-dried Tomato Tear and Share Rolls, Berry Foam","ingredients":[{"isHeader":true,"content":"Ingredients"},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Preparation Before Demo"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"250 g asparagus, woody ends removed"},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Sun-dried Tomato Tear and Share Rolls"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"220 g water"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 tsp sugar"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"2 tsp dried instant yeast"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"500 g strong white bread flour"},{"isHeader":fals